    "description_zh": "文字内容：\n人生易老天难老，岁岁重阳。今又重阳，战地黄花分外香。\n一年一度秋风劲，不似春光。胜似春光，寥廓江天万里霜。",
    "description_en": "Text:\nLife is finite, yet heaven endures; year after year comes the Double Ninth. Today again is the Double Ninth, and the yellow blossoms on the battlefield are especially fragrant.\nEach year the autumn wind blows with force; it is unlike the light of spring, yet surpasses spring, as the vast river-and-sky stretch beneath ten thousand miles of frost.",
