    "description_zh": "文字内容：\n天高云淡，望断南飞雁。不到长城非好汉，屈指行程二万。\n六盘山上高峰，红旗漫卷西风。今日长缨在手，何时缚住苍龙？",
    "description_en": "Text:\nThe sky is high and the clouds are pale, as the gaze follows the southbound wild geese into the distance. He who has not reached the Great Wall is no true hero; counting on the fingers, the journey is twenty thousand li.\nOn the summit of Liupan Mountain, red flags roll in the westerly wind. Today the long cord is in our hands; when shall we bind the gray dragon?",
